---
title: Cheesy American Beef & Pork Quesadillas with Corn-Avocado Salsa & Yoghurt
description: It’s the classic quesadillas again except we’re spicing things up with our fan-favourite all-American spice blend to coat the rich
beef and pork mince. Make it a little cheesy and add a golden corn salsa to tie it all together.
